</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>In 'Pretty Bitches,' Female Writers Examine The Words That Undermine Women</b>   <b data-is-speakable><em>Pretty Bitches, </em>a new essay collection edited by Lizzie Skurnick, explores how words that sound complimentary can actually be loaded with sexism. "These words are code," Skurnick says.</b>
